| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3185 — Recovery Inhibition (ragnarlocker)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: addd8ac8-dfd9-52ad-8912-95c0af5fb56c"
